    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                
                
            <pb n="30r"/>
            <lb n="1"/>
            <p rend="right">
               <date when="1863-05-30">Saturday 30 May 
<lb n="2"/>1863</date>
            </p>
              
              <ab>test ab</ab>
              
              <p rend="no-indent">No-indent p</p>
              
              <p>In this paragraph theres is some <foreign xml:lang="la">foreign text here</foreign></p>
              <p>There is an addition here: <add place="marginleft">Some added text in margin left.</add></p>
              <p>There is an addition here: <add place="marginright">Some added text in margin right.</add></p>
              <p>There is an addition here: <add place="margintop">Some added text in margin top.</add></p>
              <p>There is an addition here: <add place="marginbottom">Some added text in margin bottom.</add></p>
              
            <lb n="3"/>
            <p>My Dear <persName>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>HW</abbr>
                     <expan>Horace Waller</expan>
                  </choice>
               </persName>
            </p>
              <milestone unit="line" rend="half-line"/>
              <p>There is an addition here: <add place="margintop">Some more added text in margin top.</add></p>
            <lb n="4"/>
            <p>We send 
<lb n="5"/>back the books with  
<lb n="6"/>many thanks for 
<lb n="7"/>the use <space extent="5" unit="chars"/>of them. 
<lb n="8"/>they are somewhat 
<lb n="9"/>damaged <space extent="5" unit="words"/> by cockroaches
<lb n="10"/>and one is not 
<lb n="11"/>at hand, possibly 
<lb n="12"/>it may hence gone 
<lb n="13"/>down - I mean 
<lb n="14"/>the volume of "All 
<lb n="15"/>the year round<supplied>"</supplied> 

<hi rend="upsidedown">For some reason there is some vertical text here.</hi>
               <pb n="30v"/>
               <lb n="1"/>I retain <persName>Keble</persName> for 
<lb n="2"/>a little longer.</p>
            <lb n="3"/>
            <p>I am sorry that 
<lb n="4"/>you did not 
<lb n="5"/>succeed according 
<lb n="6"/>to all our wishes 
<lb n="7"/>and your own 
<lb n="8"/>I guess you uttered 
<lb n="9"/>some of your 
<lb n="10"/>terrific puns on 
<lb n="11"/>the way &amp; made 
<lb n="12"/>
               <persName>Procter</persName> ill. I 
<lb n="13"/>escaped relapse 
<lb n="14"/>myself by holding 

    <pb n="31r"/>
               <lb n="1"/>in my breath as 
<lb n="2"/>I read them. send 
<lb n="3"/>a few more I wish 
<lb n="4"/>to try if they will 
<lb n="5"/>exorcise the cockroaches 
<lb n="6"/>Better luck next 
<lb n="7"/>time for you all 
<lb n="8"/>I hope <persName>Meller</persName> will 
<lb n="9"/>cure <persName>Procter</persName> as 
<lb n="10"/>quickly as he did 
<lb n="11"/>his own case. 
<lb n="12"/>Yesterday for 
<lb n="13"/>the first time 
<lb n="14"/>I walked a little 

    <pb n="31v"/>
               <lb n="1"/>without feeling as 
<lb n="2"/>if I should faint 
<lb n="3"/>this may be the 
<lb n="4"/>effects of the iron 
<lb n="5"/>which I have taken 
<lb n="6"/>three times.</p> 
            <lb n="7"/>
            <p>With good wishes 
<lb n="8"/>for you all I am &amp;c</p>
            <lb n="9"/>
            <p rend="center">
               <persName>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>DL</abbr>
                     <expan>David Livingstone</expan>
                  </choice>
               </persName> His Mark <!-- here DL draws a little Cross AJS 12/1 --></p>


